column1: Table of all the aphids sampled for the study in order to collect different H. defensa strains
Samples with incomplete information or uncertainties were removed from this table
sample_id: unique identifier for each aphid clonal line
site: general name covering multiple samples from the same location (roughly 200m diameter circle)
plant_species: host plant from which the sample was collected
aphid_species: species name of the collected sample
extracted_DNA: was the DNA extracted and used for symbiont identification? (0: no / 1: yes)
notes: Relevant information on the sample. In this cleaned version of the dataset without incomplete samples it only indicates lines that we failed at maintaining alive in laboratory conditions
Buchnera_presence: was the presence of Buchnera aphidicola confirmed by PCR? (0: no / 1: yes)
Hamiltonella_presence: was the presence of Hamiltonella defensa confirmed by PCR? (0: no / 1: yes)
